It has been quiet...so I shall introduce myself. I play a 31 level
Barbarian Warrior on Veeshan who has slowed down in the land of Norrath to
explore lands that were a bit too scary or far off to truly enjoy. Right
now, I am in Rathe Mountains with my companion, Reece Pendell, a level 31
bard, killing hill giants here and there...oh what great revenge it is to
see them fall!

Are there any warriors out there who have gotten all the Crafted Armor yet?
Specifically, the breastplate?

Lalana A'vori---Veeshan
